description: Keep query keys stable and isolate transport contracts from UI usage.
alwaysApply: true
---

# Query Key and API Contract Rule

- Query keys must be stable, serializable, and colocated with the owning slice.
- Fetchers and mutations must live outside components.
- Do not leak raw transport DTOs across the UI without intent.
- Use mapper functions when backend contracts do not match UI needs.
- Invalidate caches narrowly and intentionally.
- Do not mirror server state into zustand.